    <name>Timecard</name>
    <summary>Track time beautifully.</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            Timecard allows you to track how much time you spend on tasks.
            It offers a clean, responsive one-window interface that allows you to
            quickly configure your time tracking, and then hides away in the system tray
            until you need it again.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Start and pause time tracking from application window or system tray.</li>
            <li>Stop timer and save to log with activity notes.</li>
            <li>View, sort, and edit time log entries.</li>
            <li>Customizable time log path.</li>
            <li>Hides to system tray.</li>
            <li>Quit protection helps prevent accidentally closing while tracking time.</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

    <content_rating type="oars-1.0" />

